	__ARM_ARCH_6T2__, __ARM_ARCH_6M__, __ARM_ARCH_7__,
	__ARM_ARCH_7A__, __ARM_ARCH_7R__, __ARM_ARCH_7M__.
	Change the conditionals to __SOFTFP__ || __ARM_EABI__
	for -mfloat-abi=softfp to work.

